name: Full Spectrum 13B
description: The Full Spectrum series of images were made by taking very high resolution scans of old nature guide books & zooming in to reveal color & pattern in the micro-landscapes of the CMYK half-tone printing resulting in minimalist, pointillistic optical color fields. Best viewed as large as possible for full immersion. Full Spectrum 13B (2021), PNG image, 7200x7200 pixels, 600dpi
